text.autoconfig.bingbingwahoo.title: Bing Bing Wahoo Config
text.autoconfig.bingbingwahoo.option.blj: How the Backwards Long Jump should behave.
DISABLED - BLJ is disabled, cannot be used.
RAPID_FIRE - Allows for long jumps and BLJs
without releasing jump or crouch in between jumps.
text.autoconfig.bingbingwahoo.option.max: Maximum velocity of a long jump.
text.autoconfig.bingbingwahoo.option.lon: Multiplier used for speed of long jumps.
text.autoconfig.bingbingwahoo.option.fli: Multiplier for the speed of flips and backflips.
text.autoconfig.bingbingwahoo.option.all: Allow wall jumping from normal jumps
Enable wall jumping out of a normal jump.
text.autoconfig.bingbingwahoo.option.bac: Enables backflipping, triggered by jumping out of a crouch.
text.autoconfig.bingbingwahoo.option.gro: Enable diving while on the ground.
DISABLED - Ground Pounds are disabled, and cannot be used.
DESTRUCTIVE - The same as ENABLED, but the Ground Pound will cause destruction.
